  "time_ut": 1660807337,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2018\u0dc0\u0db3\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d8b\u0dab\u2019\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1 \u0d91\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dad \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0da7 100 \u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dae\u0d9a \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The 'monkey flu' vaccine is not 100 percent effective",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The head of the World Health Organization, Rosemond Lewis, explains that the immunization vaccine given to prevent the infection of the 'monkey flu' virus is not 100 percent successful.",
        "'Monkey flu' is an intermediate vaccine between chickenpox and smallpox. Therefore, the immunization vaccine developed for smallpox and chicken pox is given to prevent 'monkey flu' infection.",
        "In order to prevent monkey flu infection, several countries (including America and western countries) are giving immunizations. It is reported that people who have received the vaccine have also been infected with the virus. Accordingly, the vaccines given are not 100 percent successful,' Rosemond Lewis has pointed out.",
        "The World Health Organization has explained that the 'monkey flu' virus is spreading all over the world in an unusual way because the virus has been severely mutated. By now, the virus has spread to 92 countries and 35,000 infected people have been found worldwide. Deaths are reported as 12.",
        "Meanwhile, in Paris, the capital of France, a pet dog of the 'Grey Hound' type was infected with the 'monkey fever' virus, and the World Health Organization said that it is keeping an eye on it.",
        "This is the first time that the 'monkey flu' virus has spread from a human to an animal. The World Health Organization is concerned about this by speculating that if the virus that infects pets from humans is re-infected from pets to humans, it will take a horrible mutated form.",
        "The owners of the dog infected with 'monkey flu' in France are a gay couple. Both of them are infected with the virus. According to American doctors, 'monkey flu' is a virus that spreads more among gay men."
      ],
